   Backer Wins Mazola
                                                                                                       

   Best Foods awarded its $10 million to $15 million Mazola
account to Backer Spielvogel Bates. Backer will take ad
responsibility for Mazola margarine and corn oil, as well as
Mazola no-stick cooking spray and Karo syrup.
   The account had previously been handled by Saatchi &amp;
Saatchi Advertising. Both New York agencies are units of
Saatchi &amp; Saatchi Co. Best Foods is a unit of CPC
International.
   Best Foods, which is based in Englewood Cliffs, N.J., also
named Backer to handle its grocery products unit's spot TV
buying assignment. It named BBDO, an Omnicom agency, to
handle its network TV buying job. BBDO was also awarded
several new product assignments.
